arol]]''\n| {{sort|Aird|Carol Aird}}\n| {{sort|Haynes|[[Todd Haynes]]}}\n| Executive producer\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Carol Reviews |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/carol |website=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=11 February 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160212005727/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/carol |archivedate=12 February 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Truth (2015 film)|Truth]]''\n| {{sort|Mapes|[[Mary Mapes]]}}\n| {{sort|Vanderbilt|[[James Vanderbilt]]}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Cate Blanchett on Her Embarrassment of Riches With 'Carol' & 'Truth' |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/truth-2015 |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=10 July 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161213123824/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/truth-2015 |archivedate=13 December 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Manifesto (2015 film)|Manifesto]]''\n| Various\n| {{sort|Rosefeldt|[[Julian Rosefeldt]]}}\n| 13 roles\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/12/cate-blanchett-manifesto-julian-rosefeldt-armory-1201756470/ |title=Cate Blanchett In \u2018Manifesto\u2019: Julian Rosefeldt\u2019s Stunning Film Installation is a Masterclass in Performance \u2014 Review |last=Dry |first=Jude |publisher=IndieWire |accessdate=15 December 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216172445/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/12/cate-blanchett-manifesto-julian-rosefeldt-armory-1201756470/ |archivedate=16 December 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=row | 2016\n| ''[[Voyage of Time]]''\n| Narrator\n| {{sort|Malick|[[Terrence Malick]]}}\n| Documentary\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Voyage of Time: Life's Journey (2016) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/voyage_of_time_lifes_journey |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=17 May 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104013021/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/voyage_of_time_lifes_journey/ |archivedate=4 November 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" scope=\"row\" | 2017\n| ''[[Song to Song]]''\n| Amanda\n| {{sort|Malick|[[Terrence Malick]]}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Song to Song Reviews |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/song-to-song |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=17 May 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317031450/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/song-to-song |archivedate=17 March 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Thor: Ragnarok]]'' \n| [[Hela (comics)|Hela]]\n| {{sort|Waititi|[[Taika Waititi]]}}\n| \n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Thor: Ragnarok: Cate Blanchett, Jeff Goldblum, and more join cast |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/05/20/thor-ragnarok-cate-blanchett-jeff-goldblum-tessa-thompson? |first=Anthony |last=Breznican |work=[[Entertainment Weekly]] |date=20 May 2016 |accessdate=20 May 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160522001832/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/05/20/thor-ragnarok-cate-blanchett-jeff-goldblum-tessa-thompson |archivedate=22 May 2016 }}</ref>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"3\" scope=\"row\" | 2018\n| ''[[Ocean's 8]]'' \n| Lou\n| {{sort|Ross|[[Gary Ross]]}}\n|\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|title=First Look: Sandra Bullock, Cate Blanchett, Sarah Paulson, Rihanna Ride Together in 'Ocean's 8' Photo |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oceans-8-cast-photo-sandra-bullock-cate-blanchett-sarah-paulson-rihanna-team-first-look-969355 |first=Ashley |last=Lee |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=30 January 2017 |accessdate=20 May 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207085906/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oceans-8-cast-photo-sandra-bullock-cate-blanchett-sarah-paulson-rihanna-team-first-look-969355 |archivedate=7 February 2017 }}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[The House with a Clock in Its Walls (film)|The House with a Clock in Its Walls]]''\n| {{sort|Zimmerman|