 2017 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=122543 |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date=September 2, 2014 |accessdate=March 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Where'd You Go, Bernadette (film)|Where'd You Go, Bernadette]]'' \n| {{sort|Fox|Bernadette Fox}}\n| {{sort|Linklater|[[Richard Linklater]]}}\n| \n| style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cate-blanchett-talks-star-whered-839925|title=Cate Blanchett in Talks to Star in 'Where'd You Go, Bernadette?' Adaptation|publisher=TheHollywoodReporter.com|first=Borys|last=Kit|date=12 November 2015|accessdate=10 July 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=row style=\"background:#FFFFCC;\" | TBA\n| ''[[Nightmare Alley (upcoming film)|Nightmare Alley]]'' {{dagger}}\n| {{sort|Ritter|Lilith Ritter}}\n| {{sort|del Toro|[[Guillermo del Toro]]}}\n| Filming\n| style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref>[https://deadline.com/2019/09/rooney-mara-guillermo-del-toro-nightmare-alley-bradley-cooper-cate-blanchett-fox-searchlight-1202710574/ Rooney Mara Joins Guillermo Del Toro\u2019s \u2018Nightmare Alley\u2019 At Fox Searchlight]</ref>\n|}\n\n== Stage ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Year\n!scope=\"col\"| Production\n!scope=\"col\"| Venue\n!scope=\"col\"| Role(s)\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| Notes\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\" | {{abbr|Refs.|Reference}}\n|-\n! scope=row | 1992\n| ''[[Electra]]''\n| [[National Institute of Dramatic Art]]\n| Electra\n| Directed by [[Lindy Davies]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\"newyorker\"/>\n|-\n! scope=row | 1992\n| ''[[Top Girls]]''\n| [[Sydney Theatre Company]]\n| Patient Griselda/Nell/Jeanine\n| First role at the [[Sydney Theatre Company]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|<ref name=\":2\">{{Cite web|url=http://www.biography.com/people/cate-blanchett-9214915#early-career |title=Cate Blanchett |publisher=Biography |accessdate=17 May 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/2017041919