{"title_page": "Manuchekhr Dzhalilov", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Manuchekhr Dzhalilov\n| fullname    = Manuchekhr Nasrulloyevich Dzhalilov\n| image       =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1990|9|27}}\n| birth_place = [[Hisor]], Tajikistan\n| height      = {{height|m=1.77}}\n| currentclub = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]\n| clubnumber  = 63\n| position    = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| youthyears1 ={{0|0000}}\u20132008\n| youthclubs1 = [[FC Lokomotiv Moscow|Lokomotiv Moscow]]\n| years1 = 2009\u20132010\n| clubs1 = [[FC Lokomotiv-2 Moscow|Lokomotiv-2 Moscow]]\n| caps1  = 44\n| goals1 = 8\n| years2 = 2011\u20132014\n| clubs2 = [[FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk|Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk]]\n| caps2  = 86\n| goals2 = 10\n| years3 = 2015\u20132017\n| clubs3 = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]\n| caps3  = 47\n| goals3 = 59\n| years4 = 2018\n| clubs4 = [[Sriwijaya F.C.|Sriwijaya]]\n| caps4  = 30\n| goals4 = 7\n| years5 = 2019\n| clubs5 = [[Persebaya Surabaya]]\n| caps5  = 14\n| goals5 = 1\n| years6 = 2020\u2013\n| clubs6 = [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]]\n| caps6  = 2\n| goals6 = 3\n| nationalyears1 = 2007\n| nationalyears2 = 2011\u2013\n| nationalteam1  = [[Tajikistan national under-17 football team|Tajikistan U17]]\n| nationalteam2  = [[Tajikistan national football team|Tajikistan]]\n| nationalcaps1  = \n| nationalcaps2  = 30\n| nationalgoals1 = \n| nationalgoals2 = 17\n| manageryears1  =\n| managerclubs1  =\n| pcupdate = 16:12, 12 April 2020 (UTC)\n| ntupdate = 16:33, 19 November 2019 (UTC)\n}}\n\n'''Manuchekhr Nasrulloyevich Dzhalilov''' ({{lang-tg|\u041c\u0430\u043d\u0443\u0447\u0435\u04b3\u0440 \u04b6\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432}}, {{lang-ru|\u041c\u0430\u043d\u0443\u0447\u0435\u0445\u0440 \u041d\u0430\u0441\u0440\u0443\u043b\u043b\u043e\u0435\u0432\u0438\u0447 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432}}; born 27 September 1990) is a [[Tajiks|Tajik]] professional [[Association football|football]] player who currently plays as a [[forward (association football)|forward]] for [[FC Istiklol]].\n\n==Career==\n\n===Club===\nPrior to the start of the [[2015 Tajik League|2015]] season, Dzhalilov joined reigning [[Tajik League]] champions [[FC Istiklol]].<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ru:\u0412\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043a\u0438\u043d \u0438 \u041a\u0430\u0448\u0443\u0431\u0430 \u0434\u0435\u0431\u044e\u0442\u0438\u0440\u0443\u044e\u0442 \u0432 \u0447\u0435\u043c\u043f\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0442\u0435 \u0422\u0430\u0434\u0436\u0438\u043a\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0430|url=http://sport.kg/main_news/20616-verevkin-i-kashuba-debyutiruyut-v-chempionate-tadzhikistana.html#.VkTEunbNy71|website=sport.kg|publisher=sport.kg|accessdate=12 November 2015|language=Russian|date=5 March 2015}}</ref> At the end of Dzhalilov's first season with FC Istiklol he won the [[2015 Tajik League|league]], earning the League's Top Goalscorer and Player of the Year in the process.<ref name=\"PotY15\"/>\n\nIn December 2017, it was rumored Dzhalilov had agreed a one-year contract with Indonesian [[Liga 1 (Indonesia)|Liga 1]] side [[Sriwijaya F.C.|Sriwijaya]],<ref>{{cite web|title=Sriwijaya FC Rekrut Pemain Terbaik Piala AFC 2017|url=http://www.indosport.com/sepakbola/20171205/sriwijaya-fc-sukses-rekrut-pemain-terbaik-piala-afc-2017|website=indosport.com|publisher=Indosport|accessdate=5 December 2017|language=Indonesian|date=5 December 2017}}</ref> with Sriwijaya confirming his arrival on 17 December 2017,<ref>{{cite web|title=Review Dzhalilov_Manu|url=https://www.facebook.com/sriwijayafc/photos/a.124448602998.101840.52712087998/10155869992677999/?type=3&theater|website=facebook.com|publisher=Facebook \u2013 Sriwijaya F.C.|accessdate=19 December 2017|date=17 December 2017}}</ref> and Istiklol his departure on 4 January 2018.<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ru:\u041c\u0430\u043d\u0443\u0447\u0435\u0445\u0440 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043b\u0438\u043b\u043e\u0432 \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0434\u043e\u043b\u0436\u0438\u0442 \u043a\u0430\u0440\u044c\u0435\u0440\u0443 \u0432 \u0418\u043d\u0434\u043e\u043d\u0435\u0437\u0438\u0438|url=http://fc-istiklol.tj/index.php?view=1&news=3024|website=fc-istiklol.tj|publisher=FC Istiklol|accessdate=4 January 2018|language=Russian|date=4 January 2018}}</ref>\n\nFollowing his release from [[Persebaya Surabaya]] at the end of the 2019 season, Dzhalilov featured for [[FC Istiklol|Istiklol]] in their first friendly of 2020, a 2-1 defeat to [[FK Kokand 1912|Kokand 1912]] on 9 January 2020.<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0418\u0441\u0442\u0438\u043a\u043b\u043e\u043b \u043f\u0440\u043e\u0432\u0435\u043b \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0442\u0440\u043e\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u043c\u0430\u0442\u0447 \u0441 \u041a\u043e\u043a\u0430\u043d\u0434\u043e\u043c-1912 |url=http://fc-istiklol.tj/index.php?view=1&news=4334 |website=fc-istiklol.tj/ |publisher=FC Istiklol |accessdate=9 January 2020 |language=Russian |date=9 January 2020}}</ref>\n\n===International===\nDzhalilov was a member of Tajikistan U17 football team at the [[2007 FIFA U-17 World Cup]],<ref>{{FIFA|274892}}</ref> making his senior team debut on 2 September 2011 against [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/preliminaries/asia/matches/round=257791/match=300172551/index.html|title=2014 FIFA World Cup Brazil\u2122 - Matches - Tajikistan-Uzbekistan - FIFA.com|first=|last=FIFA.com|date=|website=FIFA.com|accessdate=27 September 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Career statistics==\n\n===Club===\n{{updated|match played 12 April 2020}}<ref name=\"NFT Stats\"/><ref>{{cite web|title=M.Dzhalilov|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/manuchekhr-nasrulloyevich-dzhalilov/118542/|website=soccerway.com/|publisher=Soccerway|accessdate=30 January 2015}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Club\n!rowspan=\"2\"|Season\n!colspan=\"3\"|League\n!colspan=\"2\"|National Cup\n!colspan=\"2\"|Continental\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n!colspan=\"2\"|Total\n|-\n!Divisi